& [SLMOllamaSidecarAdapterSkeletonContract] is the source-only contract for Ollama sidecar compatibility
  + [contract_uuid] is b4104fd0-3c6e-40ff-a15c-f51748f42f62
  + [slice_id] is SLM-55
  + [depends_on] is SLM_LM_Studio_Sidecar_Adapter_Contract, SLM_Sidecar_Task_Prompt_Contract
  + [status] is verified_wsl

  & [Purpose] is to prepare Ollama-compatible sidecar exchange without live network execution
    = must: build an Ollama /api/chat style request from SidecarPromptEnvelope
    = must: include the same task_contract and response contract boundaries as LM Studio
    = must: keep stream false for deterministic v0 parsing
    = must: parse Ollama assistant message content through the validated sidecar parser
    = must: return ProviderSuggestion evidence only
    - never: execute a network call in this slice
    - never: mutate the semantic graph directly

  & [OllamaRequest] is the source-only request surface
    + [endpoint] defaults to http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/chat
    + [model] is adapter configuration
    + [messages] include system and user messages
    + [options.temperature] is low by default
    + [options.num_predict] is bounded by configuration
    + [stream] is false

  & [RuntimeProjection] is the Rust source surface
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs OllamaSidecarConfig
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs OllamaChatRequest
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs to_ollama_chat_request
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs parse_ollama_provider_suggestions_validated
    + [proof_route] is WSL cargo test and regression harness

  ! [Slice55SourceComplete] is accepted
    @ [source_gate] passed python slm_project/tools/slm_source_gate_check.py
    @ [wsl_cargo_test] passed 28 library tests and 3 slm_demo tests
    @ [regression_harness] passed slm_regression_harness_ok
    @ [request_test] Ollama request embeds task_contract and uses stream false
    @ [parser_test] Ollama response message.content is parsed through validated sidecar parser
